OVERVIEW: Enable test coverage for a scheme

USAGE: xcodeproj-cli enable-test-coverage [--project <project>] [--workspace <workspace>] [--verbose] [--dry-run] <scheme-name> [--targets <targets>]

ARGUMENTS:
  <scheme-name>           Name of the scheme to configure

OPTIONS:
  -p, --project <project> Path to .xcodeproj file (default: looks for
                          *.xcodeproj in current directory)
  -w, --workspace <workspace>
                          Path to .xcworkspace file
  -V, --verbose           Enable verbose output with performance metrics
  --dry-run               Preview changes without saving
  --targets <targets>     Comma-separated list of specific targets to collect
                          coverage for (default: all targets)
  --version               Show the version.
  -h, --help              Show help information.

